I '''Kali Deryav''' si ek deryav mashkar la sud-estutni [[Europa]]te thai la [[Anatoliya]]te. Maladyovel la [[Mediterani Deryav]]asa ando [[Bosforo]] thai andi [[Marmara Deryav]] vi la [[Azov Deryav]]asa ando [[Tangipen Kerch]]. O baripen si 422,000 km² thai o bareder axor si 2210 m. I bareder len so chhorel andi Kali Deryav si i [[Dunarya]].

Le thema ke riga la doryavake si [[Turkiya]], [[Bulgariya]], [[Rumuniya]], [[Ukraina]], [[Rusiya]], thai [[Jorjiya]] (vi i [[Abkhazia]]). O [[Krimeya]]ko [[pashdvip]] si ek autonomikani Ukrainiyaki republika.

Importante forurya pashal i deryav si: [[Istanbul]] (o purano [[Constantinople]] thai [[Byzantium]]), [[Burgas]], [[Varna]], [[Konstanca]], [[Yalta]], [[Odessa]], [[Sevastopol]], [[Kerch]], [[Novorossiysk]], [[Sochi]], [[Sukhumi]], [[Poti]], [[Batumi]], [[Trabzon]], [[Samsun]].

== Anav ==
Le akanutne anava si amboldimata le lavenge Μαύρη Θάλασσα ([[grekikanes]]: "Kali Deryav"), sar: [[Turkikani ćhib|turkikanes]] Kara Deniz, [[Rusikani ćhib|rusikanes]] Чёрное море, [[Bulgarikani ćhib|bulgarikanes]] Черно море, Cherno more, [[Jorjikani ćhib|jorjikanes]] შავი ზღვა, shavi zghva, [[Ukrainikani ćhib|ukrainikanes]] Chorne More,  [[Rumunikani ćhib|rumunikanes]] Marea Neagră, [[Laz ćhib|laz]] Ucha Zuğa (vai xarnes Zuğa "Sea"), [[Ubykh ćhib|Ubykh]] {{IPA|ʃʷaʤa}}.

